						<summary>

						<p>Rock called Tallēṭiguṇḍu in the river-bed 1(1/2) km North-West of the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Virōdhikṛit, Māgha śu. 1, Friday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. It refers to the Dēvaprithivi-Mahā and. It also mentions Mallikārjuna some individual Mutti figures a <hi rend="italic">kavi</hi> (poet).</p>						

